{
  "module": "02-arkdata.md",
  "group": "02 — Data Persistence (ArkData)",
  "apiCount": 5,
  "apis": [
    {
      "name": "@ohos.data.preferences (用户首选项)",
      "purpose": "Key-Value轻量级数据持久化，支持number/string/boolean及其数组类型，提供get/put/delete/flush等操作",
      "anchor": "@ohosdatapreferences-用户首选项",
      "status": "found"
    },
    {
      "name": "@ohos.data.relationalStore (关系型数据库)",
      "purpose": "基于SQLite的关系型数据库，提供表创建、增删改查、SQL执行、事务管理等完整数据管理能力",
      "anchor": "@ohosdatarelationalstore-关系型数据库",
      "status": "found"
    },
    {
      "name": "@ohos.data.sendableRelationalStore (共享关系型数据库)",
      "purpose": "为关系型数据库提供Sendable支持，实现ValuesBucket/Asset在taskpool并发线程间的跨线程传递（API 12+）",
      "anchor": "@ohosdatasendablerelationalstore-共享关系型数据库",
      "status": "found"
    },
    {
      "name": "@ohos.data.ValuesBucket (数据集)",
      "purpose": "定义数据集键值对类型ValueType和ValuesBucket，作为DataShare场景的数据插入集合（API 10+，仅Stage模型）",
      "anchor": "@ohosdatavaluesbucket-数据集",
      "status": "found"
    },
    {
      "name": "@ohos.data.dataSharePredicates (数据共享谓词)",
      "purpose": "提供DataShare查询筛选条件的谓词，支持equalTo/and/or/like/between/orderByAsc/limit等数据库筛选操作（API 10+，仅Stage模型）",
      "anchor": "@ohosdatadatasharepredicates-数据共享谓词",
      "status": "found"
    }
  ],
  "notableFindings": [
    "All five APIs import from @kit.ArkData but under different namespaces: preferences, relationalStore, sendableRelationalStore, dataSharePredicates, plus direct type imports for ValuesBucket",
    "@ohos.data.ValuesBucket defines a base ValueType = number|string|boolean for DataShare, while relationalStore has a richer ValueType including Asset/Assets/Uint8Array/bigint — these are distinct types in different namespaces",
    "preferences does NOT guarantee process concurrency safety; XML/GSKV storage modes added in API 18",
    "sendableRelationalStore requires API 12+ and is specifically designed for taskpool multi-thread scenarios",
    "dataSharePredicates serves as a backend-agnostic predicate; when used with RDB it effectively maps to RdbPredicates semantics"
  ],
  "missingApis": []
}

{
  "module": "03-file.md",
  "group": "03 — Core File Kit (File I/O)",
  "apiCount": 4,
  "apis": [
    {
      "name": "@ohos.file.fs (文件管理)",
      "purpose": "基础文件操作，包括文件/目录管理、读写、属性、复制、删除、文件流、文件监听等完整 IO 能力",
      "anchor": "ohosfilefs-文件管理",
      "status": "found"
    },
    {
      "name": "@ohos.file.picker (选择器)",
      "purpose": "系统文件选择器，支持文档/音频/图片的选择与保存，通过 DocumentViewPicker/AudioViewPicker 拉起系统界面",
      "anchor": "ohosfilepicker-选择器",
      "status": "found"
    },
    {
      "name": "@ohos.file.environment (目录环境能力)",
      "purpose": "获取系统预授权目录的沙箱路径（下载、桌面、文档目录），2in1 设备可用",
      "anchor": "ohosfileenvironment-目录环境能力",
      "status": "found"
    },
    {
      "name": "@ohos.file.fileuri (文件URI)",
      "purpose": "文件 URI 与沙箱路径的转换，提供 FileUri 类进行 uri-path 双向转换和属性获取",
      "anchor": "ohosfilefileuri-文件URI",
      "status": "found"
    }
  ],
  "notableFindings": [
    "@ohos.file.picker 的 PhotoViewPicker 从 API 12 开始废弃，图片/视频选择应使用 @kit.MediaLibraryKit 的 photoAccessHelper.PhotoViewPicker",
    "@ohos.file.picker 的 DocumentViewPicker 和 AudioViewPicker 推荐使用带 UIAbilityContext 参数的构造函数，无参构造存在概率性拉起失败",
    "@ohos.file.environment（getUserDownloadDir/getUserDesktopDir/getUserDocumentDir）仅 2in1 设备可正常调用，其他设备返回 801 错误码",
    "@ohos.file.fs 的 open/read/write/stat 等接口从 API 22 开始支持传入 URI，之前仅支持沙箱路径",
    "picker 三类 URI（应用沙箱、文档、媒体）使用方式不同：文档 URI 通过 fileUri 转沙箱路径后用 fileIo 操作，媒体 URI 需用 photoAccessHelper.getAssets 临时授权访问"
  ],
  "missingApis": []
}

{
  "module": "04-photo-access.md",
  "group": "04 — Photo Access (Media Library)",
  "apiCount": 7,
  "apis": [
    {
      "name": "@ohos.file.photoAccessHelper (相册管理模块)",
      "purpose": "获取 PhotoAccessHelper 实例，用于查询和操作相册中的图片视频资源",
      "anchor": "ohosfilephotoaccesshelper-相册管理模块",
      "status": "found"
    },
    {
      "name": "PhotoViewPicker",
      "purpose": "拉起系统图库选择界面，支持图片/视频选择，返回具有永久授权的 URI",
      "anchor": "photoviewpicker",
      "status": "found"
    },
    {
      "name": "AlbumPickerComponent",
      "purpose": "嵌入相册列表 ArkTS 组件 (API 12+)，无需权限即可访问公共相册列表，需配合 PhotoPickerComponent 使用",
      "anchor": "albumpickercomponent",
      "status": "found"
    },
    {
      "name": "PhotoPickerComponent",
      "purpose": "嵌入媒体文件选择 ArkTS 组件 (API 12+)，无需权限即可实现图片/视频选择功能",
      "anchor": "photopickercomponent",
      "status": "found"
    },
    {
      "name": "FetchResult",
      "purpose": "文件检索结果集，提供 getCount/getFirstObject/getNextObject/getAllObjects/close 等遍历方法",
      "anchor": "fetchresult",
      "status": "found"
    },
    {
      "name": "PhotoAsset",
      "purpose": "媒体文件资产接口，提供 get/set/commitModify/getThumbnail/clone 等属性和方法",
      "anchor": "photoasset",
      "status": "found"
    },
    {
      "name": "MediaAssetManager",
      "purpose": "媒体资产管理类，提供 requestImage/requestImageData/requestMovingPhoto/requestVideoFile/cancelRequest 等静态方法",
      "anchor": "mediaassetmanager",
      "status": "found"
    }
  ],
  "notableFindings": [
    "所有 API 从 '@kit.MediaLibraryKit' 统一导入，API 23 前需要从 '@ohos.file.photoAccessHelper' 等分别导入",
    "PhotoViewPicker.select 返回的 photoUris 具有永久授权，可通过 getAssets 使用，无需 READ_IMAGEVIDEO 权限",
    "PhotoPickerComponent/AlbumPickerComponent 为无权限嵌入组件，从 API 12 开始支持",
    "getAssets/getThumbnail/MediaAssetManager 请求方法需要 ohos.permission.READ_IMAGEVIDEO 权限",
    "commitModify/clone 需要 ohos.permission.WRITE_IMAGEVIDEO 权限",
    "MediaAssetManager 从 API 11 开始支持",
    "PhotoViewPicker 重复拉起前需要销毁前一个实例"
  ],
  "missingApis": []
}

{
  "module": "05-image.md",
  "group": "05 — Image Kit (Image Processing)",
  "apiCount": 7,
  "apis": [
    {
      "name": "@ohos.multimedia.image (图片处理)",
      "purpose": "图片解码、编码、编辑、元数据处理和图片接收等能力",
      "anchor": "ohosmultimediaimage-图片处理",
      "status": "found"
    },
    {
      "name": "PixelMap",
      "purpose": "位图对象，包含像素数据和图片信息，支持读取/写入像素数据、裁剪、缩放、旋转、翻转等操作",
      "anchor": "pixelmap",
      "status": "found"
    },
    {
      "name": "ImagePacker",
      "purpose": "图片压缩和编码类，将 ImageSource/PixelMap/Picture 编码为压缩数据流或写入文件",
      "anchor": "imagepacker",
      "status": "found"
    },
    {
      "name": "ImageSource",
      "purpose": "图片源类，用于获取图片信息、解码为 PixelMap 或 Picture、读写 Exif 属性",
      "anchor": "imagesource",
      "status": "found"
    },
    {
      "name": "image.createImageSource",
      "purpose": "通过 uri/fd/ArrayBuffer/rawfile 创建 ImageSource 实例",
      "anchor": "imagecreateimagesource",
      "status": "found"
    },
    {
      "name": "image.createPixelMap",
      "purpose": "通过像素数据和图像属性创建 PixelMap 对象",
      "anchor": "imagecreatepixelmap8",
      "status": "found"
    },
    {
      "name": "image.PackingOption",
      "purpose": "图片编码选项，指定格式、质量、缓冲区大小、动态范围等参数",
      "anchor": "packingoption",
      "status": "found"
    }
  ],
  "notableFindings": [
    "导入方式为 import { image } from '@kit.ImageKit'，not from '@ohos.multimedia.image'",
    "PixelMap/ImageSource/ImagePacker 使用完成后必须调用 release() 释放 native 内存",
    "PixelMap 序列化大小上限 128MB，按宽*高*每像素字节数计算",
    "createPixelMapFromPixels/createEmptyPixelMap 是替代旧 createPixelMap/createPixelMapSync 的推荐 API",
    "packToData/packToFile 是替代已废弃 packing 方法的推荐 API",
    "HDR 图片需通过 desiredDynamicRange 参数控制解码/编码动态范围",
    "PackingOption 编码格式支持 image/jpeg, image/webp, image/png, image/heic, image/gif 等"
  ],
  "missingApis": []
}

{
  "module": "06-notification.md",
  "group": "06 — Notification Kit",
  "apiCount": 7,
  "apis": [
    {
      "name": "@ohos.notificationManager (NotificationManager模块)",
      "purpose": "通知管理器模块，提供发布、更新、取消通知，创建/获取/移除通知渠道，查询通知使能状态等能力",
      "anchor": "ohosnotificationmanager-notificationmanager模块",
      "status": "found"
    },
    {
      "name": "notificationManager.publish",
      "purpose": "发布或更新通知，相同ID和标签则替换原有通知",
      "anchor": "notificationmanagerpublish",
      "status": "found"
    },
    {
      "name": "NotificationRequest",
      "purpose": "通知请求对象，包含内容、ID、渠道类型、按钮、角标、自定义铃声等属性",
      "anchor": "notificationrequest",
      "status": "found"
    },
    {
      "name": "NotificationSlot",
      "purpose": "通知渠道，控制通知的提醒方式（级别、振动、铃声、角标等）",
      "anchor": "notificationslot",
      "status": "found"
    },
    {
      "name": "NotificationContent",
      "purpose": "通知内容的联合类型，支持普通文本、长文本、多行文本、图片、系统实况窗",
      "anchor": "notificationcontent",
      "status": "found"
    },
    {
      "name": "notificationManager.requestEnableNotification",
      "purpose": "拉起通知授权弹窗获取用户通知授权（Stage模型，需在loadContent成功后调用）",
      "anchor": "notificationmanagerrequestenablenotification10",
      "status": "found"
    },
    {
      "name": "notificationManager.setSlot",
      "purpose": "未找到该API——通知渠道管理使用 addSlot/getSlot/removeSlot/removeAllSlots，不支持 setSlot",
      "anchor": "notificationmanagersetslot",
      "status": "missing"
    }
  ],
  "notableFindings": [
    "setSlot 不是实际存在的API，通知渠道通过 addSlot(type)/getSlot(slotType)/removeSlot(slotType)/removeAllSlots() 管理",
    "requestEnableNotification 从 API 12 起必须传入 UIAbilityContext 参数；旧版无参重载已废弃",
    "publish 错误码 1600004=全局禁用，1600005=渠道禁用",
    "通知去重通过 appMessageId 实现，24小时内生效",
    "Wearable 不支持 setBadgeNumber（返回801），isDistributedEnabled 在 Wearable/TV 恒为 false"
  ],
  "missingApis": [
    "notificationManager.setSlot"
  ]
}
